Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[♪ opening theme song playing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[wind howling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Looks like it keeps\Ngoing forever from up here.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't even see\Nall the way to the bottom.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NIt's a 3,000-meter drop.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is the deepest canyon\Non the entire continent.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The climb may have felt slow,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but the elevation here\Nis immense.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You've been here before.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-So how do we cross it?\N-[wind gushes]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] The wind is quite strong.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Flying magic is too risky.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Again with the crossing.\NAgain with the wind.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] If we head upstream,\Nwe could cross at the river.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But we would\Nhave to forge through{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}a treacherous mountain range.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A lengthy and dangerous detour.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We could go downstream,\Ncouldn't we?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Only one problem seaside.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There's a cliff that's also\N3,000 meters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Apparently,\Nit's a sight to behold{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}if you'd like to drop by.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] No, thank you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NEither way, at this rate,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}it's going to take us\Na bare minimum of two weeks{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to safely cross the canyon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}My feet can't take it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not like we have\Nany other choice, right?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Hmm...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I imagine\Nit's in the final stages.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's in the final stages?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}For now,\Nlet us continue upstream.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If we're lucky, we'll come upon\Na nifty shortcut.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our shortcut.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] I had a good feeling.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] There's a bridge?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You should've led with that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] At last,\Nlooks like he's finished it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[footsteps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Gehen.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] It's been\Na while, Frieren.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Seems your\Nbridge project was a success.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[GEHEN] Indeed.\N-[FERN] You know him?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] This is Gehen,\Nthe skilled dwarven carpenter{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}who spent the past two centuries\Nbuilding this bridge.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] So dedicated.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm surprised\Nto see it finished.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A bridge this well-made\Nshould be a major crossing,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}yet I haven't heard it mentioned\Nor recorded on any maps.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I assumed that meant\Nit was still in progress.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And perhaps we would find you\Nin the last stretch.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Frieren...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}there is still one more problem\Nfor me to solve.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[loud whooshing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[wind gushes]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Right on cue.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A flock of bird monsters\Nhave been stirring up{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}powerful gusts of wind.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Some merchants came through{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}on their journey\Nto the so-called Golden Land.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They were blown over\Nthe side, wagon and all.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You can slay them,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-but they'll only keep coming.\N-[wings flapping]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They've built a nest{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and made this canyon\Ntheir playground.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}In doing so, they've rendered\Nmy bridge useless.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Fortunately, the nest is located\Non this side.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Could you help me\Nsolve my problem?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't let 200 years\Nof work go to waste.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}As for payment?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] A spell that lets you\Nflip pancakes perfectly.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have all the ingredients.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A breakfast of dreams\Nis just one chore away.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[Fern gasps]\N-[STARK] Uh...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-You have a deal.\N-[Fern grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[wind howling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}According to Gehen,\Nwe should be drawing near.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] That path is\Nawfully close to the edge.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Watch where you step.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Your bodies would be\Nimpossible to find.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Why did Gehen\Ntake it upon himself{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to build a bridge here\Nin the first place?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm sure regret had\Nsomething to do with it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL] I see.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, it's still\Nunder construction.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's a shame.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Do you know\Nwhen it will be finished?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] I'm not sure\Nit will ever be.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I ran out of funds.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Doesn't that sting?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}All the time in the world\Nand none of the money.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Tell us, Gehen,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}why are you so determined\Nto build a bridge out here?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] In a happier time,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}this is where my village sat.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Still would if it weren't\Nfor the demons.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Unfortunately for us,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the closest army was stationed\Nin a city across the canyon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This bridge\Ncould've saved them,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but too little, too late.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Should've thought\Nto build it sooner.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[footsteps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL]\NPerhaps this can help.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our reward\Nfrom a distant noble.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Demons stole a treasured sword\Nand my party helped reclaim it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] This is a lot of money.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thank you,\Nbut I can't accept this.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have nothing suitable\Nto offer you in exchange.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL] You have this bridge.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Huh? You're a human.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}By the time\NI finish construction,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you'll have died of old age.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Himmel chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL] Then Frieren\Nwill accept your repayment.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Frieren gasps softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Give her at least\Na thousand years.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Build it to last.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] That I can do.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You can count on me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Here they are.\NLet's begin.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[whooshing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Gehen...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We took care of the monsters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Thank you, Frieren.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now folks can freely\Ncross the canyon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}My work here is done.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What now?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Do you have any other\Nbig projects ahead of you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Hmm...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm building my peace.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A quiet life in my village.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[MAN 1]\NHey, look who's back.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[MAN 2]\NAnd just in time for dinner.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's amazing news, Gehen.\NThis calls for celebration.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[GEHEN] Frieren...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Two hundred years\Nis more than enough time{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}for a village to be built anew.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Of course.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NWell, shall we be off, then?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern groaning]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Is something wrong?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] We may or may not be\Nlow on travel funds.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Ah!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You didn't leave us with enough\Nto get through a single week.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Frieren groans softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[sighs] Mistress, you can't\Nkeep wasting all our money.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not like it matters now.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What are we buying\Nin the middle of a snowfield?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mm. Don't you worry.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have just the solution.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NWe're changing course.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Prepare your pockets.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is this?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Not a village,\Nthat's for sure.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maybe some adventurer camp?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[MAN] All right, boys,\Nlet's get out there{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and give it all we've got.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[ALL] Yeah!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Where have you taken us\Nthis time?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Stark is correct that\Nit's a camp for adventurers.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Those seeking\Nholy snow crystals.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Am I supposed to know\Nwhat that is?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NIt's a mineral{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}produced in the snowfields\Nof this region.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They're used to create\Nmagic potions.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is the only place\Nin the world{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}where they can be mined,\Nso they fetch a high price.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I get what we're doing.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now ready your pickaxes, ladies,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}because these holy snow crystals\Naren't gonna mine themselves!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You've seen so much\Nyet remain so naive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Holy snow crystals{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}aren't something you can\Nsimply stumble upon.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's why\Nthey're so expensive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Then how are we gonna\Nmake any money here?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Have you ever been\Nto a marketplace{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}that caters exclusively\Nto adventurers?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You'll find it very interesting.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] It looks like your run\Nof the mill marketplace to me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now look closer.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A whole silver\Nfor a loaf of bread?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's more than ten times\Nthe market price.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}For their clientele is as rich\Nas they are hungry.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mining is hard work,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but their bounties are worth\Ntheir weight in gold.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It only makes sense\Nprices are higher here.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Let's change careers.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There are two primary reasons{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}holy snow crystals sell\Nfor such a high price.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The first of which\Nis their rarity.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The second reason\Nis that this region{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}is teeming with savage monsters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Do you see\Nwhere I'm going with this?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Judging by what\Nthey charge for bread,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}monster slaying requests would\Nfetch a rather hefty reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Right as always, Fern.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[fire crackling]\N-[MAN] Up here.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There's a massive mineral vein\Nthat only us locals know about.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'd like you to defeat\Nthe monster dwelling there.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}One more thing.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once you've slain the beast,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}please set up\Nan anti-personnel barrier.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Anti-personnel?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes. I don't want\Nthe wrong people{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}getting too close.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Understood. We'll take the job.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN]\NI'm grateful for the work,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but an anti-personnel barrier{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}feels like\Na fairly unusual request.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It takes time to gather\Nthe manpower{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and funds required\Nfor a mining operation.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you wish to claim\Na plot of land{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but lack the resources to begin,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}an anti-personnel barrier\Nis your best option.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern sighs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] In any case,\Nwe have a monster to slay.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] There it is.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That thing is giant.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Be sure to keep your guard up.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We were hired for this job\Nas a last resort.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If the adventurers at camp{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}could've taken care of this,\Nthey would have.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Lack caution, and you'll die.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's only fair that the risk\Nmatches the reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Let's get to work.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[monster growls]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[roaring]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mistress, it's reacting\Nto our mana.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What an annoying detail.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark grunting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK]\NIt's faster than it looks.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Stark, run!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's the first step of my plan.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That I can do!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] Higher.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark pants, gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[grunting, panting]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark yells]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark pants, grunts]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark yells]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark sighs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] They made us\Nwork for that reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[both chuckle softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mistress Frieren?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[FRIEREN] Quiet.\N-[Fern gasps]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[growling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Great. From bad to worse.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's safe to assume\Nour last opponent{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}was the lord of this area.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Nearby monsters must have\Nsensed its mana fading{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and gathered here\Nto investigate.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Any more plans, Frieren?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I have the energy\Nto carry you two and run{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}if we wanna go that route.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Far too late for that.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] We're surrounded.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[growling]\N-Indeed, but even if we weren't,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}we would still need\Nto slay them all{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}in order to complete the job.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Think you have\Nenough mana, Fern?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I should fare just fine.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] We've no other choice.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN]\NThe Chivalric Order of Norm.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It was clear\Nthey were moving somewhere,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}so we followed them\Nto find out where and why.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We weren't expecting\Nto find you three.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Of course not,\Nthough we appreciate the help.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We've done nothing\Ncompared to you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Mm?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Master Norm says\Nthat we're in your debt.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That you have done much\Nto help our cause.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I suppose this makes us even.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[captain chuckles]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[CAPTAIN] Farewell.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[hoofbeats receding]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't believe they rode\Nall the way here. Impressive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Agreed. That squad is charged{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}with watching over\Ntheir entire territory.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Even if it's little by little,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the Northern Plateau\Nis changing.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's long past sunset, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How about we set up\Ncamp here tonight?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[fire crackling]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Frieren groans softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Mistress Frieren,\Ntime to wake up.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Come see this.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Frieren groans softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] Just five more hours.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] Fine,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-but you'll have to freeze.\N-[groans]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-It's worth waking up for.\N-[Frieren groans]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] The way the light\Nshimmers through the crystals...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The vein is beautiful\Nin the morning sun.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Frieren gasps softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FRIEREN] You're right.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And to think\Nwe only made a detour{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to bolster our travel funds.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wasn't expecting to come upon\Nsuch a feast for the eyes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[EISEN] It's beautiful.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL] This is\Nmore than enough reason{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to see our quest\Nthrough to the end.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[HIMMEL] If we defeat\Nthe Demon King,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}a time will come when anyone\Ncan enjoy this beautiful sight.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not just anyone could make\Nthis harsh journey.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But in this era, more people\Nwill see this wonder{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}than in any era before.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's a strange feeling.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] It really is beautiful.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Yeah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yet soon enough,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}it will be broken into rubble\Nby human hands.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's a bit sad,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}but no one can stop\Nthe march of time.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Take it in.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once you have, we'll erect\Nthe barrier and head back.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[MAN] A job well done.\NThank you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Here's your reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm just relieved we can finally\Npreserve the vein.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Preserve?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, you aren't intending\Nto mine it later?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It was in my childhood here\Nthat I decided my fate.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}One glimpse\Nof that beautiful sight{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and I knew I wanted\Nto become an adventurer.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now it's safe.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thanks for protecting\Nthe wonders of my home.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Of course.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Protecting other people's homes\Nis an important job, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, it is.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The more I look back on it now,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the surer I am\Nthat Master Heiter{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}protected my home, too.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's true that war left\Nmy physical home in ruins.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Even so, because of him,\NI have the precious memories.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Stark chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK]\NThose are what count.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}When I told you the story\Nabout me fleeing my home,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you didn't let it impact\Nyour opinion of me{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}in the slightest.\NYou continued to believe in me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Nothing's changed.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You always encourage me\Nand push me forward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Why?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] Because that's what\NMistress Frieren would do.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[♪ closing theme song playing]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}-[Stark groans]\N-[Fern sighs]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[FERN] Mistress Frieren,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}you know the prices here\Nare astronomical,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}yet you went shopping?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A magic item like this\Nis a rare find.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just like that, we're back\Nto barely scraping by.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I had a feeling\Nthis would happen,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}so I hid our cut of the reward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Seriously?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You never let me down, Fern.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And that is why\Nyou are my student.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[Fern chuckles softly]{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[STARK] Always a mystery.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, shall we be off, then?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[LERNEN] This is Edel,\Na second-class mage.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}She specializes\Nin mental magic.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I asked her to accompany me\Nso she could reexamine the area.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}She obtained some\Nnew information.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Information you, for one,\Nwill surely find valuable.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Denken, your hand...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll transfer the memories\Nto you.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[DENKEN] Go ahead.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[LERNEN] And with that,\NI leave you to your work.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Your duty is straightforward.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maintain and manage{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the barriers surrounding\Nthe golden land.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That is your charge.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You shall do nothing more\Nand nothing less.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[EDEL] Denken...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Her grave is just a hole\Nin the ground.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[DENKEN] I'm aware.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[EDEL] He intends to die.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yet I feel a touch of envy,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}for never in my wildest dreams\Nwould I defy Mistress Serie.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}[LERNEN] The final\Nand the strongest{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}of the Seven Sages awaits him.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Macht of the Golden Land.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The valiant Denken\Nshall fight to the bitter end{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}to save his gleaming home.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Fate pulls him like\Nhe's the hero in a fairy tale.{\b0}
